name: Ultimate Island Trek
description: Experience the thrill of the Whitsundays with the Ultimate Island Trek, a high-octane adventure perfect for solo riders seeking excitement and natural beauty. This tour combines the exhilaration of jetskiing with the serenity of a tropical island getaway. Enjoy a delicious poolside lunch featuring woodfired pizzas, salads, and chips as you relax by the pool or on the beach. Ideal for adrenaline junkies and nature lovers, this trek offers a unique opportunity to explore the stunning Whitsunday Islands and encounter local wildlife, including sea turtles and seasonal humpback whales.
includes:
Approximately 3 hours of thrilling jetskiing
Poolside pizza lunch
Informative and entertaining commentary by qualified tour guide
Sea turtles, dugongs, seabirds and seasonal humpback whales (July – September) are often encountered on tours
All riding apparel including lifejackets, rash tops/thermal tops, wetsuit shorts, polarised sunglasses, riding hats and sunscreen provided
All photos of your tour provided free of charge on Facebook
Free courtesy bus pick up and drop off within Airlie Beach area
highlights:
Jetski to a beautiful Whitsunday Island
Enjoy a woodfired pizza lunch by the pool
Explore numerous islands and resorts
Encounter sea turtles and seasonal humpback whales
Experience a thrilling 70km trek
price_tiers: Solo Rider: A$495 per jetski | QLD Public Holiday surcharge: A$20 per jetski
ideal_for: Adventurous solo riders with a love for water sports and nature
custom_section_1:
• What to Bring:**

• Casual clothes

• Bathers

• Sunscreen

• Towel

• Camera

• *Important Notes:**

• *YOUR JETSKI ADVENTURE CHECKLIST:**

Understand English
Must be able to swim wearing a lifejacket
Solo riders only with a minimum age of 16 years and over for the Ultimate Island Trek tour
Above average fitness level and confidence in open waters
Big smiles and sense of adventure!!

• *THINGS YOU NEED TO KNOW:**

Our ADVENTURE TOURS operate daily in most weather conditions
A reasonable level of fitness is required, as some conditions can be physically demanding
Please consider your suitability to your chosen tour
Bring along swimmers, towel and sunscreen (like a day at the beach)
A dry bag will be provided for your towel, phone/camera
Thorough safety briefing and demonstrations provided by qualified tour guides
Fully supervised at all times by one or two guides, depending on numbers
Weight restrictions apply, maximum 200kg per jetski
If under 18 years of age, an indemnity form must be signed by parent or guardian prior to tour
Group bookings are available
Gift vouchers are available
As a wind guide: 10 knots – smooth, dry ride, 15 knots – partly smooth some choppy small waves, 20 knots plus – choppy water spray and large waves. Management reserve the right to change itinerary or times in extreme weather conditions.
Tour is only available for private charter (minimum 6 jetskis)

name: Two Island Safari Tour
description: Embark on an exhilarating adventure with the Two Island Safari Tour, perfect for thrill-seekers looking to maximize their time on the water. Experience the stunning Whitsunday Islands as you jet ski through the scenic waterways around Daydream and South Molle Islands. This tour offers a unique blend of breathtaking scenery and heart-pounding excitement, making it ideal for adventurous travelers eager to explore marine life and capture unforgettable moments.
includes:
Approximately 2 hours of action packed jetskiing
Informative and entertaining commentary by qualified tour guide
Sea turtles, dugongs, seabirds, and seasonal humpback whales (July – September) encounters
All riding apparel including lifejackets, rash tops/thermal tops, wetsuit shorts, polarised sunglasses, riding hats, and sunscreen
Power snacks and bottled water
All photos of your tour provided free of charge on Facebook
Free courtesy bus pick up and drop off within Airlie Beach area
highlights:
2 hours of thrilling jetskiing
Scenic views of Daydream and South Molle Islands
Opportunity to see marine life such as sea turtles and dugongs
Free tour photos on Facebook
Convenient courtesy bus service
price_tiers: Per Jetski: A$329 | Per Person Twin Share: A$164.50
age_requirements: Minimum passenger age of 12 years and over
ideal_for: Adventurous travelers seeking a thrilling and scenic water experience

name: Airlie Adventure Tour
description: Experience the thrill of driving your own jetski around the stunning Whitsunday Islands. This tour combines adrenaline-pumping adventure with eco-friendly exploration, perfect for thrill-seekers and nature enthusiasts alike. Spot sea turtles and other marine life as you navigate the beautiful bays of Airlie Beach. This accessible tour is ideal for families, couples, and groups looking for a unique way to enjoy the coastal scenery.
includes:
Approximately 1.5 hours of jetskiing
Informative and entertaining commentary by qualified tour guide
Sea turtles, dugongs, seabirds and seasonal humpback whales (July – September) sightings
All riding apparel including lifejackets, rash tops/thermal tops, wetsuit shorts, polarised sunglasses, riding hats and sunscreen
Bottled water
All photos of your tour provided free of charge on Facebook
Free courtesy bus pick up and drop off within Airlie Beach area
highlights:
Drive your own jetski
View the Whitsunday Islands
Explore Airlie’s beautiful bays
Sea turtle encounters
Suitable for all skill levels
Accessible tour
price_tiers: Per Jetski: A$259 | Per Person Twin Share: A$129.50 | QLD Public Holiday surcharge: A$20 per jetski
